<div class="app-card-container">
    <h1 style="color: black;">About Me</h1>
  <div class="card">

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "http://mtloafer.nebo.edu/sites/mtloafer.nebo.edu/files/styles/large/public/DSCN3904_0.JPG?itok=D9KtHUd7", width: 300, alt: "profile image" %>
        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                ></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>So I am a very new person to the world of coding. This was my first major coding class and so i was very new at this</p>

        <p>So for me being able to make something like this is beyond amazing. And that is me</p>
        <p> Adam Belliston age: 14/15 (my birthday was 8/31 so i turned 15 recently)</p>

        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Cornabys
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Coding
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Mt Loafer Elementary School
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Salem Junior High School
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Salem Hills High School
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
           